    "id": 6,
    "slug": "how-a-black-hole-and-a-shredded-star-could-light-up-a-galaxy",
    "cat": "Astrofísica",
    "catCls": "astrofisica",
    "img": "https://www.universetoday.com/article_images/fig1-13-1078x516_20260417_205916.jpg",
